{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"竹沟石榴红","authors":["牛雅杰"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":5,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹沟石榴红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔叙事诗〕  牛雅杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇同志任中共中央中原局书记时，一九三九年曾住在河南省竹沟镇，亲手在窗前种下一棵石榴树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水有情呵山有意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山水水想着你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少奇同志来竹沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军崖畔脚步留；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他知道这是烈士殉难处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今花满石榴树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红艳艳的山石榴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸引他眼神扯住他袖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折下一枝压窗前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇水、施肥洒热汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说稀奇呵可真稀奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二年树高过房脊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝儿高呵树身瘦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花朵朵开得稠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人传呵个个喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说长得象少奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少奇离开竹沟时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶上的露珠象泪丝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔情思磨亮了石头路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人争着来看石榴树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹沟根据地这般好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豺狼怎能不伸魔爪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民党部队开来两三万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制造了著名的“竹沟大惨案”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尸横遍地哭野风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草芽芽都被血染红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民党军官去摘石榴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶上落下大石头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几个大兵忙赶到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石块如雨从树上掉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸死一帮官和兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说这树有神灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了一个骑兵连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乒乒乓乓把树砍……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说奇怪也真奇怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个谜儿实难猜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民党军队刚开拔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上又冒出石榴芽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众松土又浇水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石榴树叶象翡翠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然知道河湾稠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没想到水倒流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命风卷雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂雷恶闪打少奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的竹沟根据地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜间抹得黑漆漆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家烈属受审查，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士陵墓被炸塌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜那棵石榴树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也被暴徒连根除！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连根除了还不算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖地三尺根找净；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又用石块填平地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头缝里浇水泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍下的石榴穿人衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牌子上写着刘少奇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游罢南队游北队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处召开批斗会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批罢斗罢劈成柴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧成灰烬化尘埃……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长河尽管有弯曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕竟滚滚东流去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬去春来喜泪注，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首先想起石榴树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明还是那棵树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青枝绿叶窗前矗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是眼花不是梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真真切切是实景。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人传十十传百，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹沟老小都赶来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石榴树呵不是从天落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老赤卫队员用心血来养活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天批斗石榴树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偷剪一枝种在后山坡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一家人轮流去站岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手护着树苗心发烫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一听说打倒“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连夜移栽在老地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石榴树呵石榴树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把竹沟人民的深情铸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石榴树呵快快长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长在竹沟人民的心坎上……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"name":"捍卫毛泽东思想工人赤卫队上海总部（赤卫队）","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}